{"tid":2431352,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"緬甸保安部隊再開槍鎮壓　人權組織稱18人死亡","createTime":"2021-03-03T14:50:06.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-03T14:52:31.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a6613759c0cebcfa3cb4af1ac7deaec02335fe6b","tid":2431352,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T14:50:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1578592-20210303.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1578592-20210303.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=UjOWczzRfTNgHoC3e3JiX4GitI067obQ02bu1xQE4oc%3D&h=95119470\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1578592-20210303.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=3f17c827\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1578592-20210303.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n緬甸反對軍事政變的示威持續。外電引述人權組織報道，保安部隊在各地開槍鎮壓示威者，增至19人死亡。<br />\n<br />\n在最大城市仰光、第二大城市曼德勒和另一個城市蒙育瓦都有人中槍。<br />\n<br />\n被推翻及扣押的總統溫敏早前被加控兩項罪名。律師說，其中一項是違反憲法，最高可判監三年。<br />\n<br />\n東盟外長昨天舉行視像會議商討緬甸局勢，並無突破進展，他們呼籲緬甸各方克制，但只有4個成員國，敦促釋放被扣押的國務資政昂山素姬等人。"},{"pid":"43e63e5e77053e254f33f2891a2364a96b0776eb","tid":2431352,"uid":51583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T14:52:31.000Z","msg":"#ACTION<br />\n#ACTION<br />\n#ACTION"}]}